name: Maui Listana
text: With this additional info,ibig sabihin for the dictator,he really considered LNMB as a cemetery for heroes. So to have him put there, gusto ng pamilya niya na tingin sa kanya hero. What the photos showed was no simple soldier's burial rites. Pati sa ganun bagay, sinungaling at manloloko. At this point, we should already expect all the worst from this family. Wala talang konsyensya. Bakit ba nagugulat pa tayo sa kasamaan na pinapakita?
